<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-02-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-02-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="78" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d78">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">761.9311/2–2148: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Smith</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-02-21">February 21,
                                1948</date>.<lb/>[Received February 21—12:31 p. m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>353. Tass communiqué appearing Soviet press today announces extension
                            nonaggression pact USSR and China,<note n="58" xml:id="d78fn58">Signed
                                at Nanking, August 21, League of Nations Treaty Series, vol. <hi rend="smallcaps">clxxxi</hi>, p. 101.</note> points out treaty
                            has been renewed three times since 1937 and that in accordance its
                            provisions treaty will automatically be renewed for additional 2-year
                            period if neither party gives notice of denunciation within 6
                            months.</p>
                        <p>Dept. pass Nanking as 7.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Smith</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>